_Title note: replace the placeholders with a real range. Use the day after the last post ended as the start date, and today as the end date. Example: `Things I Read: 1-13 Apr 2026`._

_Excerpt note: write a factual sentence under 140 characters that tells a reader what they get here, not just how many links there are. Example: "Recent reading on AI hype, self-hosting, and tools that feel more brittle than they should."_

_Write 1-2 sentences here on what kept showing up in this pile, what mood the reading had, or why these were the pieces that stayed with you._

_If a couple of items obviously belong together, split this into multiple `<section class="reading-notes-section">` blocks and add `<h2>` headings. If not, leave it as a single stream._

